      <li><strong>MRI scan:</strong> €150-250</li>
      <li><strong>Dental cleaning:</strong> €30-50</li>
      <li><strong>Emergency room visit:</strong> €50-150</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
      <p class="text-blue-800">
        <strong>Sofia healthcare tip:</strong> The best private hospitals in Sofia include Acibadem City Clinic, Tokuda Hospital, and Pirogov Hospital (public but high quality for emergencies). Many doctors in these facilities speak English and accept international insurance for direct billing.
      </p>
